name: hirotosan
description:
mr hiroto was a homeless person. he sat behind a lake and People threw coins at him .one day a coin tossed by someone fell into the lake and hiroto just jumped into the lake and swam to the bottom of the lake and saw the fishes They gathered around him because of the coin! 
hiroto felt like a king after that! he was collecting his coins and swam to the bottom of the lake just for the fishes and He ruled...Days passed and the lake became ordinery to him ordinery he collected more coins and went to an ocean tied the bag of coins around his waist swam to the deep
All the fish gathered around him he was revel untill He could no longer hold his breath ..The weight of the coins and the depth of the water didn't allow him to reach the surface ..He could not drop his coins there The water filled his lungs and he died.. After a while, the coins rusted the algae covered them and they became cloudy...The fish were scattered too ..Years passed and no one even knew about him
